          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">crossovers</ENAMEX> per chromosome, so <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">all three</NUMEX> chromosomes in
          most of the 
          rec12 mutant meioses are
          <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">achiasmatic</ENAMEX>.
        
        
