          polysomic aneuploids (having additional copies of
          individual chromosomes), and diploids [ <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">38 39 44</NUMEX> ] . In 
          <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">S.</ENAMEX> pombe the haploids and diploids
